an angle of [`\theta =`] [`[$theta]`] [`^{\circ}`] with the horizontal. The distance from A to C is [`r_{AC} =`] [`[$rAC]`] [`m`].

[`v_{fish} =`][___]{"$vel"}[`m/s`]  
[`a_{fish} =`][___]{"$accel"}[`m/s^2`] 



END_PGML


